### ==================================================
### HEALTH CHECK ENDPOINTS
### ==================================================
### NOTE: These endpoints do not require authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Full Health Check
# Checks database, redis, memory, and disk
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Liveness Probe
# Checks if the app is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/live

### Readiness Probe
# Checks if the app is ready to receive traffic
# Validates critical dependencies (database, redis)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready
